data.enText: to remove the plug of a piece of electrical equipment from the electricity supply

simple_means.memory_skill: un 打开，解开，弄出 + plug 塞子，插头 → 拔去（塞子、插头）

tr: pull the plug of (electrical appliances) and render inoperable
example: unplug the hair dryer after using it

value.def: If you unplug an electrical device or telephone, you pull a wire out of a socket so that it stops working.

example.ex: I had to unplug the phone.
